OL,6,FA man has been jailed for raping a
OL,7,Fhomeless woman in Cardiff city centre
OL,8,Fin an attack which he filmed on his
OL,9,Fphone.
OL,11,FLiam Stimpson physically beat the
OL,12,Fwoman, and after raping her tripped
OL,13,Fher up, punched her and kicked her to
OL,14,Fthe head.
OL,16,FCCTV and mobile phone footage showed
OL,17,FStimpson rape and violently assault
OL,18,Fthe victim during the early hours of
OL,19,FWednesday, December 27, 2023.
