OL,6,FHe had been out celebrating his 24th
OL,7,Fbirthday when he attacked the woman
OL,8,Funderneath a railway bridge near
OL,9,FCardiff Central railway station.
OL,11,FHe initially assaulted her with a
OL,12,Fmetal object and repeatedly punched
OL,13,Fher, before subjecting her to a
OL,14,Fprolonged and violent sexual assault
OL,15,Fwhich he filmed using his mobile phone.
OL,17,FAfter she managed to escape by running
OL,18,Faway, Stimpson chased her down,
OL,19,Fknocked her to the floor and continued
OL,20,Fhis brutal physical assault upon her
OL,21,Fin the middle of the city centre.
