OL,6,FTwo key witnesses, a cleaner from a
OL,7,Fbar and a delivery driver, intervened
OL,8,Fand police were called.
OL,10,FWithin half an hour of being called,
OL,11,FStimpson was arrested in Caroline
OL,12,FStreet and has been in custody ever
OL,13,Fsince.
OL,15,FStimpson, from Llanrumney, Cardiff,
OL,16,Fwas found guilty after trial of two
OL,17,Fcounts of rape, causing a person to
OL,18,Fengage in sexual activity without
OL,19,Fconsent and causing grievous bodily
OL,20,Fharm with intent. He pleaded guilty to
OL,21,Fpossession of cannabis.
