OL,6,FThe court heard the defendant had a
OL,7,Fnumber of previous convictions
OL,8,Fincluding theft, attempted theft,
OL,9,Fattempted robbery and possession of a
OL,10,Fcontrolled drug.
OL,12,FOn Monday, 3 June, he was sentenced to
OL,13,F15 years in prison, of which he will
OL,14,Fserve two thirds in custody. He was
OL,15,Falso made subject to sex offender
OL,16,Fnotification requirements and a
OL,17,Frestraining order indefinitely.
