OL,6,FIn a victim personal statement read to
OL,7,Fthe court by prosecutor Nicola Powell,
OL,8,Fthe victim said: "I would like to say
OL,9,Fthis has destroyed my life. I cannot
OL,10,Fsleep at night, I can picture
OL,11,Feverything and I keep seeing his face.
OL,12,FThis has changed my whole opinion
OL,13,Ftowards men. I want this male to end
OL,14,Fup in prison for what he has done to
OL,15,Fme.
