OL,6,F"I worry about him doing this to
OL,7,Fanother female. I am in fear of this
OL,8,Fmale being released from prison and
OL,9,Fattacking me again, both sexually and
OL,10,Fphysically. It affected me greatly. I
OL,11,Fam unable to socialise with others at
OL,12,Fpresent, I want to be alone to block
OL,13,Fout what's happened to me."
OL,15,FIn mitigation, Ruth Smith said her
OL,16,Fclient was very sorry for the violence
OL,17,Fhe used against the victim. She asked
OL,18,Fthe court to have regard for totality.
