OL,6,FJudge Jenkins told the defendant:
OL,7,F"This was not consent. This was
OL,8,Fdomination by you to her... You have
OL,9,Fnot shown one scintilla or remorse or
OL,10,Fsympathy for your victim. You forced
OL,11,Fthe victim to relive events of that
OL,12,Fnight and the effect on her in the
OL,13,Fwitness box is palpable...
OL,15,F"You degraded and humiliated her...and
OL,16,Fforced her to crawl like a dog while
OL,17,Fyou filmed it. You completely
OL,18,Fhumiliated her and took away the last
OL,19,Founce of dignity from her."
