OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing,
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Katherine Barry,
OL,8,Ffrom South Wales Police, said:
OL,9,F"Stranger attacks such as these are
OL,10,Fextremely unusual in Cardiff but in
OL,11,FLiam Stimpson we had a dangerous
OL,12,Findividual.
OL,14,F"The level of violence he used, and
OL,15,Fdegradation of the victim was
OL,16,Fhorrendous. He is an absolute danger
OL,17,Fto women.
